tourBios.curYrHigh: Finished T14 at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament, tying with three others. Didn't earn his full exemption when he fell in a three-hole playoff to determine the final two spots. Will play this season with conditional status.
tourBios.carHigh: 2014: Played in four PGA TOUR China events but failed to make a cut. Highlight of the season came in August when he opened with a 68 at the Yulongwan Yunnan Open.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA Tour China Serie was T40th in 2015 at the Hainan Open.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 92nd in Par Breakers on the PGA Tour China Series.
